數據，兩種疫苗皆「證明了自身地安全性，也能有效預防武肺症狀」，但小組也提出了警告「兩隻疫苗都缺乏高齡族群的接種數據，而共病症狀方面的資訊也並不足夠。」小組專家暗示疫苗有機會導致其他情況發生。截至目前只有輝瑞/BNT、牛津/AZ、強生3種疫苗獲得世衛的認可。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:38:57.000Z","msg":"等香港打完，新有數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:52:13.000Z","msg":"一直都係咁樣 作收集數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n死既死 冇事既就再中招"},{"pid":"173e48225641449a748be0dff1912e1421fda574","tid":2478033,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:53:17.000Z","msg":"啊翠呢排唔記得過數咩？"},{"pid":"735ea5060036c40e26b9b382420f22e082d33d9b","tid":2478033,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:55:20.000Z","msg":"數據咋？多多都比到你啦"},{"pid":"6f30b779e204043450872c714e7c5418f386f13d","tid":2478033,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T18:55:39.000Z","msg":"要數據呀&hellip;識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}